subject: College Athletics
Gymnastics
Colleges and Universities
lead_paragraph: Alex Buscaglia tied for first in Friday’s last event to lead Stanford to its fifth N.C.A.A. men’s gymnastics title and the university’s 100th national championship in all sports.
